    <para>&bibletime; is a completely free Bible study program. The
      program's user interface is built with the &qt; framework, which makes
      it run on several operating systems including Linux, Windows,
      FreeBSD and Mac OS X. The software uses the &sword; programming
      library to work with over 900 free Bible texts, commentaries,
      dictionaries and books in over 50 languages provided by the &cbs;
      and several other repositories.</para>
